    <div class="ic-container">
      <div class="evo-problem">
        <div class="evo-problem__text">
          <span class="evo-section-label">The Problem</span>
          <h2 id="proc-problem-heading">Buying Office Tech Shouldn't Be a Headache</h2>
          <p>Walking into a major retailer for office laptops often means paying for features you don't need — or getting consumer-grade plastic that breaks within 12 months.</p>
          <p>When your Perth small business needs new technology, you need reliable, commercial-grade hardware that is secure and ready to go the moment you turn it on.</p>
        </div>
