      <div class="evo-services__grid" role="list">

        <article class="evo-service-card" role="listitem">
          <span class="evo-service-card__num">Service 01</span>
          <h3>Expert Hardware Advice</h3>
          <p>We don't just sell boxes — we assess how your business actually operates. Whether your team is designing graphics in Osborne Park or crunching numbers in the CBD, we recommend the exact laptops, desktops, or servers that fit both your workflow and your budget.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="evo-service-card" role="listitem">
          <span class="evo-service-card__num">Service 02</span>
          <h3>Pre-configured &amp; Ready to Work</h3>
          <p>Forget spending half a day setting up a new employee's laptop. We supply devices fully pre-configured — bloatware-free, connected to your Microsoft 365 environment, and secured with proper endpoint protection. Out of the box and ready for business.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="evo-service-card" role="listitem">
          <span class="evo-service-card__num">Service 03</span>
          <h3>Business-Grade Networking Gear</h3>
