          </button>
          <div class="evo-faq__answer" id="proc-faq1" role="region">
            <div class="evo-faq__answer-inner">IT procurement is the process of sourcing, purchasing, configuring, and deploying the right business-grade hardware for your organisation. Perth businesses benefit from working with a local IT partner like Evotech because you get expert advice tailored to your workflow, commercial-grade devices that last, and pre-configured hardware ready to use straight out of the box — without the guesswork of buying from a retail store.</div>
